Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.47,TITILE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:12.99,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 僅僅2周就發育到這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:17.94,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為使用了促進發育的zid-02和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:20.48,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你參加了進修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:23.62,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點知識你應該知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.86,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:30.35,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一看到實物就不知不覺地興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:32.96,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.97,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我馬上去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:20.77,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹葉間射下來的陽光真刺眼呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.77,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然曬黑了會很傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:26.12,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不這樣的話就沒有夏天的感覺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.40,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 蟬蛻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:32.91,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次看到這麼令人心裡發毛的姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:36.31,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離約定的時間還有一會兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.07,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.31,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是滴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.50,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想喝什麼啊 我請客喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:50.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然使用了平時都會來一腳迴旋踢的故障自動售賣機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.28,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還連我的份也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:55.59,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.32,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:07.07,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對沒有想要撲進姐姐大人的懷裡的非分之想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:12.90,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊 你要好好注意才行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.96,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要喝什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.51,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太反常了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.99,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼美麗溫柔的姐姐大人究竟是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.72,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:28.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就決定喝椰子蘇打好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:35.19,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天姐姐大人的內衣花紋是橙色水滴 內褲是眨眼的呱太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.03,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來這出是鬧哪樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.52,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 原來是本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.74,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在了 在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.26,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.09,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.85,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 曬得好健康啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.78,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天去哪兒逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:04:00.42,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想買幾樣[廣域社會參觀]時需要用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.27,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說馬上就要到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.71,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那御坂學姐你們要去哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.45,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是學藝都市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.97,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個在加利福利亞的人工島上的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.46,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.71,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.19,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是在一個團體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.49,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到那邊我們五個人也能一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:23.33,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃飯 購物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.95,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那還有沙灘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.75,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我都興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.51,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要不要去買一件新的泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.88,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是先要買必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.40,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也還有其他很多東西要買
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.98,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在這時候有那個儲蓄卡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.89,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.39,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我只是開個玩笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:47.66,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 那件事之後有什麼進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:51.62,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天才發生的 不可能這麼快就有進展的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.69,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.58,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真關心這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.10,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有點在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:00.87,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這背後肯定還藏著更大的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.11,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什麼根據啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:05.93,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是個都市傳說獵人的直覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.93,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.13,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.49,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 傳說中的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:12.49,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有什麼事件麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.28,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.38,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是佐天同學的玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.55,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 初春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.99,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事都無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:24.86,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧 不然沒時間咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.01,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.17,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 買到了 買到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.65,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這點東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.89,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來買快用完的東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.71,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:39.84,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.98,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯煲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:46.56,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 自從跟春上同學住在一起就開始自己做飯吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.03,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們不是有一個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有一個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.65,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 昨天也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:54.77,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠用是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.28,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:00.06,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是春上同學你的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.80,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的飯量也很大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.82,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是 初春也不是一般的吃貨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:05.62,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.26,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這個怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.86,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高級的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.94,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 但 預算不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.08,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就便宜點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.79,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.87,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.49,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:27.60,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.51,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 買了個好棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:36.65,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到御坂學姐有那樣的社交能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:40.57,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想般做飯生活就要開始了喔 春上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.64,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以做可口的飯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.57,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好多種商品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.87,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 這裡的品種很齊全的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.33,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.17,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個超可愛做出來也不忍心吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.54,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.47,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:12.34,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 春上同學有看中泳裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.71,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳裝太多了 看得眼花繚亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:19.36,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次選泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.55,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我幫你選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.21,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打開了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:25.86,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.45,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件有點孩子氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.60,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.16,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.79,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有點幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.83,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.83,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就試這套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:41.62,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得御坂學姐今天情緒有點興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.48,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春你也這樣想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.80,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道發生了什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.29,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那這套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.33,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這套稍微有點過激了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:46.91,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.53,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 春上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:52.72,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買到稱心的泳衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.95,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.80,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到御坂學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.52,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個長的很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.76,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在講這話題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.85,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為真的很像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:09.32,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 該不會那是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.64,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂學姐的分身之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:19.91,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 說起相像 我曾經聽固法前輩說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:23.30,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(878,618)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:23.30,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞中有想用複製技術來製造超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.53,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.35,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複製啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:35.60,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真有學院都市風格的傳聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.68,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的有自己的複製人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.06,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是佐天同學的話 會怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:45.36,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.76,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫她幫忙做暑假作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:52.59,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她留在宿舍的話就可以瞞過宿管了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.48,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃到2人份的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:09:00.66,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很棒啊 在點餐中猶豫二選一的時候就可以二份都選啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:04.08,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 這樣的話每個人就只能吃到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.06,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.17,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.11,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是姐姐大人的話又會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.94,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己面前出現自己的複製人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.73,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:32.17,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得很像真的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:33.59,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.25,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要製作出這樣的的複製人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:52.73,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所見的 這種狀態下精神年齡就跟初生嬰兒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:57.12,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既無法理解語言 也不能自己行走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.21,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.94,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是怕再這樣下去她會感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.72,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份閒情馬上就沒有咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.40,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說要一口氣將她完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:18.05,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言語與運動 以及倫理之類的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:23.63,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}<Testment>\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\r}\N只要使用[學習裝置]向五感傳輸電氣情報的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.93,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能強制輸進大腦內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.77,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這步應該可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.86,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 關於剛才的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:32.38,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.54,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效率不會很低嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.55,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不重複調整的話就無法長久保持了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.55,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照製造順序來依次使用會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.36,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有上面的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:48.46,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能奉命行事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.15,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一天就這麼結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:59.07,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話暑假眨眼間就要結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.43,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間馬上就要過孟蘭盆節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:04.30,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 到這個時候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.35,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學園都市里並不重視這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.05,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本沒人回老家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:13.69,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不很好嗎 就因為這樣大家才能聚在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:14.93,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.40,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:21.66,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假還 很悠長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:29.30,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時間才吃早餐的人 還真有閒情逸致啊 御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:30.76,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.11,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又沒有其他事要幹 好閑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.07,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那白井她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:40.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h<Judgement>{\r}\N黑子和初春同學去幫忙[風紀委員]的夏季公募
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.09,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學她們也有其他約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:47.45,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣悶得發慌的還真是寂寞的青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.27,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要你多管閒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:52.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣你快點吃完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.59,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然這麼下去都不能收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:59.35,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯總該讓我慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.88,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真沒有要做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.57,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.73,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.81,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高興興地來翻看新刊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:21.79,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現竟然是和上周的合併刊的失落感真不是蓋的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.09,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好閑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.37,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.35,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.12,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.97,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候在找包的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.61,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間的話 就和我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我挺忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.20,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.92,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在說好閑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:47.76,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.28,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.72,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大姐姐就來陪陪你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.90,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說自己大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:03.94,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓她說吧 已經到了想裝老人家的年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.81,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.39,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 玩什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.49,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.12,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:12.22,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看老人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.50,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡　又被踢掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:16.64,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.57,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢到那麼遠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:21.31,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小學生玩一般會那麼較真嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:26.50,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀　我和你們一樣 還是孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.48,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪 惡魔 非人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:29.36,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你說個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.53,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿平角褲的惡女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.82,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:40.51,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會逞強的就只有這張嘴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.69,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 惡女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.33,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h<LEVEL5>{\r}\N總有一天我當上超能力者以後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.19,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會來報仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.55,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都會作你對手的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:55.99,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是會使用電擊的高手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:57.98,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.15,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是直君一樣的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:01.90,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:03.89,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.33,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼努力也只能出來這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.57,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始誰都是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.62,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍛煉了以後就能學會很多本事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:20.47,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 直君能和姐姐打電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:21.35,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.96,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用電擊來聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.93,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.33,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說是聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.66,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連對方在哪裡都不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.53,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:39.75,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是在海上沒有其他干擾的話也許可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:46.89,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像在城市裡到處都有太多的信號干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:50.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:51.81,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.84,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}<LEVEL UPPER>{\r}\N也有幻想御手例外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:52.63,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.41,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩抓鬼遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.98,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.30,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.79,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:58.95,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦波相近的人之間說不定能建立起網路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.86,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:07.22,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HELLO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我在說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.39,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常對話中的導入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.46,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:16.07,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂這麼判斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:17.84,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,件體號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.97,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9982號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.31,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂網也好好聯上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.87,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:35.37,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 像這麼正大光明地站著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.57,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.18,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:43.54,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微加點羞恥心不也挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.05,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加些多餘的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.09,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果產生叛亂就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.38,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說安全裝置也並不是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.81,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:58.69,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底我們根本沒有給予感情的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:03.77,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個機器也是經由那個叫布什麼的天才少女監修後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:06.41,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才終於能進行實用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.00,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子還真精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.79,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出了一身汗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:27.94,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 請問你這個徽章是在哪裡入手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.28,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在商店街的扭蛋機裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:40.63,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是轉動把手後掉出扭蛋的機型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:45.29,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過類比化 不在我能力範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.90,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:03.17,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀看呀 常盤台的女生在玩扭蛋機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.66,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是為了幫那些孩子抽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.10,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.21,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 幫我去換下零錢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.72,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 為什麼讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.35,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別反抗 她的眼神很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.80,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:29.48,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 如果你喜歡的話 我來和你交換
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.43,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 車站也有個一樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.04,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.35,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.11,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:52.29,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:53.23,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.71,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這下終於
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.19,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要用來幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:05.62,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在點燃了喜歡作品的關聯商品全部都要得到手時收藏靈魂後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:09.17,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不瞻前顧後地爆發的經歷有過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:14.86,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白像這個孩子一樣別在衣服上真的很出格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:19.73,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至都能想像出黑子那時會用多麼憐憫的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.12,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.68,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果掛在包上的話還勉勉強強可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:27.14,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:29.93,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這個點了 我們得要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.65,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.72,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水裡你能憋幾秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.51,ASIDE(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天玩得好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.41,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是暑假也不能老顧著玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.51,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要好好做作業哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:58.06,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.53,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.02,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.71,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.40,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.53,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 回家路上要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.77,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:31.07,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那股感覺是什麼 和我很像的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:36.76,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 就像是我自己力量是從外界照射在我身上一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:43.72,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.89,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.92,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.29,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:15.66,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肌肉 體力 心肺功能都沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.20,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下裡待人接物的測試合格的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.02,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差不多可以轉移到外部研究了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:28.59,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂已經學會了從點漢堡到拒絕推銷的方式了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:32.28,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自信完美地融入外界人群當中去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.95,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對該測試的必要性存有疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:41.08,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外部的世界也有些連測試都不能涉及的問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:42.04,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:45.68,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}<ORIGINAL>\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\r}\N和素體相遇的可能性也不是零
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.02,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 雖然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:51.38,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會成為實驗的阻礙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:53.97,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}<ORIGINAL>\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\r}\N素體到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.30,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.46,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}<SISTER’S>\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\r}\N妹妹們的素體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.75,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話 就是你們的姐姐大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.52,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:14.30,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是從這附近出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:39.68,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:13.23,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:16.98,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有配給的衣服 就換上那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.65,0:23:21.63,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 在到下次的實驗為止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:22.90,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:25.25,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我處理下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.34,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:32.89,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:33.79,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:34.55,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.33,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪裡都一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:37.90,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.56,SUB(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人 你在穿衣鏡前面說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:01.37,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sister's noise 探し続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:04.79,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨う心の場所を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:11.50,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重ね合った　この思いは誰にも壊せないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:21.27,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繰り返された　真実は遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:26.77,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君のその痛み　気づけないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:34.89,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの日託したその夢が　私を切り裂いても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:41.74,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何よりも大切な　希望だけ信じ貫いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.41,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰よりも近くにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.79,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その声は聴こえなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:56.31,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻み続けていた時の中で　やっと君に逢えたから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.71,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sister's noise 探し続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:03.05,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨う心の場所を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:09.30,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じ合った　同じ笑顔　必ず守ってみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.21,OP(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう　誰にも壊せないから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:01.37,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sister’s noise 不斷找尋你們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:04.79,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在內心彷徨不安的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:11.50,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意相合 這個想法 不會讓任何人破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:21.27,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過多次反復 真相依舊遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:26.77,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的那份痛楚 仍舊沒有察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:34.89,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳們期望的那個夢想　會讓我粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:41.74,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說　最重要的　是堅信著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.41,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明比任何人都還要接近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.79,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻聽不見你們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:56.31,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於在這不斷增加的時空裡與你們相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.71,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sister’s noise 不斷尋找你們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:03.05,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在內心彷徨不安的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:09.30,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意相通 同樣的微笑 我一定會守護到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.21,OP(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都無法破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:58.03,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知らない空眺めながら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:03.71,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも　いつも　君と歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:10.06,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日までとは違う未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:16.48,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃げたような気がして　探したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:22.00,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぼやけていた　視界には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:27.16,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷っていると　思い込んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:32.84,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心触れたら全て変わっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:35.13,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽きるくらい雲　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:39.28,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数えたら　また遠くに流れていった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.31,0:22:44.52,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追いかけて　見つけたよ　明日の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:48.06,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二度と来ない今　確かめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.08,0:22:51.05,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伝わった　君の思い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:56.75,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつか　きっと　私もあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:23:02.69,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲のように　そっと　そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:09.71,ED(JA),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこまでも　ずっと　ずっと　前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:58.03,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遙望著天空的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:03.71,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直和你走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:10.06,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停在昨天的不同未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:16.48,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎能見到尋找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:22.00,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呆呆的視線裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:27.16,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己迷失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:32.84,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦觸摸到心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:35.13,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會立刻破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:39.28,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厭倦的雲朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.31,0:22:44.52,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐了以後便能看到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:48.06,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的夢想不會重來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.08,0:22:51.05,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切實傳達出對你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:56.75,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一定一定我也會給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:23:02.69,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像雲一般悄悄地悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:09.71,ED(CH),NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何處 一直一直向前
